headline: CompoSecure Appoints Mary Holt as Chief Financial Officer
summary: Brings a wealth of financial leadership from world-class organizations such as Honeywell and PfizerSOMERSET, N.J., Oct. 09, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- CompoSecure, Inc. (NYSE: CMPO), a leader in metal payment cards, security, and authentication solutions, today announced the appointment of Mary Holt as Chief Financial Officer (CFO), effective the day immediately following the filing of the Company's Q3 2025 Quarterly Report. She succeeds Tim Fitzsimmons who is retiring after a distinguished career
